Class DynamicResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.faces.application.Resource
      • org.omnifaces.resourcehandler.DynamicResource

  • public abstract class DynamicResource
extends javax.faces.application.Resource
    This Resource implementation represents a cacheable dynamic resource which doesn't necessarily exist as a regular classpath resource.

    2.0
    Author:
